DATA LICENSE & ATTRIBUTION
==========================

The data files distributed in this repository's GitHub Releases — vector tiles
(*.pmtiles), the GraphHopper routing graph (gh_*.zip), and the POI, address, and
speed-limit databases (*.db) — are DERIVED FROM OpenStreetMap.

  © OpenStreetMap contributors.

They are made available under the Open Database License (ODbL) v1.0:

  - Open Database License (full text):  https://opendatacommons.org/licenses/odbl/1-0/
  - OpenStreetMap copyright & attribution:  https://www.openstreetmap.org/copyright

You are free to copy, distribute, use, and adapt these data, provided that you:

  1. ATTRIBUTE OpenStreetMap and its contributors (as above), and
  2. SHARE-ALIKE: if you publicly use an adapted/derived database, you make that
     derived database available under the ODbL.

Source / how the data was produced
-----------------------------------
These files are generated from a Geofabrik OpenStreetMap extract of the
Netherlands using open-source tooling (Planetiler for tiles, GraphHopper for the
routing graph, pyosmium for the databases). The generation scripts live in the
application's own repository under tools/. The produced data files themselves are
the assets attached to each GitHub Release here.

Scope
-----
This license applies ONLY to the data files in the Releases. The application that
downloads them is a separate work and is NOT licensed under the ODbL.
